Azure have largest no of data centres:
Azure have diff. geographies defined like : East europe ,Asia
Inside diff. Geographies it have regions.
Every regions have atleast one data centre

Geography --> Regions --> datacentre

Azure have paird datacentre to provide fault tolerance
Every regions have availibilty zones which have fault domain , update domain

To group container who share same life cycle , Azure have resource groups.
IT aggregates resource into single managable unit
